{"tid":2517031,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"宇狗條仆街放fake news","createTime":"2021-05-05T05:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T07:22:54.000Z","uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"243faa634cde6255a0d3d2d04614c1b59d9d5fb5","tid":2517031,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:10:12.000Z","msg":"下海女星身份曝光？ 人母加護亞依被爆收1億日圓拍5套AV<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2515598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2515598</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n///////////////////////<br />\n<br />\n　不過也因為太多媒體轉述消息，而且有愈來愈誇張的趨勢，所以她回應了拍AV的消息：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　簡單地一句話，就是沒那個計畫(拍AV)啦！<br />\n<br />\n　　不管聽到加護亜依的名字時你是興奮、期待還是感慨、悲傷、失望又或者是其他的情緒現在都可以放下了，本人都說不是了那就應該不是，如果你認為只是還不能公布所以加護亜依必須予以否認也沒關係，反正現在我們能做的也就只有等待，直到SOD給我們答案〜"},{"pid":"dcb240684a7d76909616835ce8d1ff8c6e6c0b11","tid":2517031,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:52:04.000Z","msg":"推到bam佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8183861004b316b73ce7f9bc70096b818cdcc054","tid":2517031,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:53:55.000Z","msg":"世清反CUP佢啦"},{"pid":"b9f634ece4837be064dc666234ffd42889fa8990","tid":2517031,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcb240684a7d76909616835ce8d1ff8c6e6c0b11","tid":2517031,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:52:04.000Z","msg":"推到bam佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:15:16.000Z","msg":"唉 推"},{"pid":"e30b474aae71982fb549cb7c09c59723515e94bc","tid":2517031,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8183861004b316b73ce7f9bc70096b818cdcc054","tid":2517031,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:53:55.000Z","msg":"世清反CUP佢啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:15:29.000Z","msg":"推到世清出動"},{"pid":"78